title: DaleyEdster
author: DaleyEdster
content: Purdey Yachts Tradesmen NFT GiveawayTo celebrate the upcoming mint of 2000 Purdey Yachts Tradesmen NFTs on 7th April 2023 we are giving you the chance to win one of 23 prizes!Prizes3 x Tradesmen NFTs (free mint)5 x OG Discord roles15 x Purdey Yachts Whitelist Spots for the upcoming mintYou can stake the NFTs to earn daily $YACHT rewards (the token for the Purdey Yachts project). You will also be able to use the Tradesmen NFTs to build a Purdey Yacht NFT.There are 5 different types of Tradesmen to collect - Carpenter, Laminator, Engineer, Tester and Captain.How to enter:1) Enter the Gleam Campaign here - https://gleam.io/competitions/SgP9F-purdey-yachts-tradesman-nft-giveaway2) Complete the required tasks.3) Complete all of the tasks to unlock a bonus entry,Duration of the Campaign: - 17th March - 6th April 2023.Announcement of winners: - 8th April 2023 on the Purdey Yachts Discord channel=======================================================Learn more about Purdey YachtsWebsite: www.purdeyyachts.netDiscord: https://discord.gg/7M2Nb5pfKDTwitter: https://twitter.com/purdey_yachtsPlease do not post your referral links or proof of participation on Bitcointalk. If you have questions, go to the Purdey Yachts Discord.
